==English==

===Noun phrase===
'''dependent variable''' (''plural'' '''dependent variables''')

# {{algebra}} In an [[equation]], the variable whose value depends on one or more variables in the equation.
#:''In the equation z = x<sup>2</sup> + y, z is the dependent variable.''

